platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Even if you dont consider yourself a cook, chances are youve been tempted to channel your inner chef after seeing one of the fun video recipes from Tasty that are all over the internet. These super-short, step-by-step cooking tutorials show how simple it can be to make everything from Cinnamon Roll French Toast to Mozzarella-Stuffed Meatballs to Apple Pie Cheesecake. The Tasty app puts more than 2,000 of these easy-to-digest videos on your iPhone or iPad.
